      "file_path": "docs/guides/onap-user/instantiate/instantiation/service_instance/index.rst",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 45,
      "message": "Let me answer.\nVID team has been working for a couple years on a new UI, which is triggered, when certain conditions are met (works a kind of pop-up). Example: macro flows with BB workflows. That UI is called \"ModernUI\". Have You noticed \"Instantiation Status\" in recent VID versions? --> ModernUI\n\nThe availability and functionality of \"ModernUI\" is controlled by VID feature flags, being a part of VID configuration, and stored in the VID container.\n\nWe`re looking at enabling that ModernUI in VID permanently.\nI have an open MR targeting that activity: https://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/vid/+/117980 \n\nYou can try and give a +1, if You like that one.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 5597,
        "name": "Damian Nowak",
        "display_name": "Damian Nowak",
        "email": "damian.nowak@nokia.com",
        "username": "deen1985"
      },
      "updated": "2021-03-05 15:20:17.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": "9974c70c_1cdb8339",
      "unresolved": true
    },
